Kurumi Kernel - tiro (NX769J / RedMagic 9 Pro, SM8650 pineapple)
Base: AOSP GKI android14-6.1 + nubia msm-kernel overlay
Build identity: kurumi@dev

Highlights:
 - Balanced power saving (WQ_POWER_EFFICIENT, PM/thermal debug off)
 - Battery tweak baked into the kernel via overlay.d
   (WALT freq smoothing + fewer VM wakeups; run by Magisk on boot)
 - Stock KMI / ABI parity (no LOCALVERSION ABI break)

Flashing: RAM-boot test first (fastboot boot boot.img), then flash this zip.
Revert battery tweak: reflash stock init_boot.
